P(X\geq m)=\sum_{r=m}^{\infty}\frac{e^{-\lambda}\lambda^r}{r!};m=0,1,...
m=1,2,...
P(X\geq m)=\int_{0}^{\lambda}\frac{e^{-u}u^{m-1}}{(m-1)!}du
